### ── SALES SERVICE (/sales) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Ortam: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev
### Akış: createOrder → (PaymentService capture) → completeOrder

### 1. Sipariş oluştur — Customer Bauer, VW Golf GTI (MUC)
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/createOrder
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000010",
  "deliveryType": "HOME_DELIVERY"
}

### 2. Siparişleri listele — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/Orders
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Siparişleri listele — Customer Bauer (sadece kendi siparişleri)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sales/Orders
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Siparişi iptal et — Customer Bauer
### orderId: 1. adımdan dönen ID'yi buraya yaz
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/cancelOrder
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}

### 5. Siparişi tamamla — Manager (ödeme sonrası manuel tamamlama)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/completeOrder
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}

### 6. Başka müşterinin siparişini iptal etmeye çalış — reddedilmeli
POST {{baseUrl}}/sales/cancelOrder
Authorization: {{customerHoffmannAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "BURAYA_ID_YAZ"
}